N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 12 ยง 332.4 - Date of hearing

State Regulations

The Psychology Practice Committee shall prepare a calendar
of disputed bills and shall arrange a time and place of hearing. At least 30
days prior to the date set for hearing, notice thereof shall be mailed to the
psychologist and carrier, advising the date, time and place of the
hearing. Notes
